                "invention-title": [
                    "Cold-resistant composite dust suppressant as well as preparation method and application thereof",
                    "耐寒复合抑尘剂及其制备方法和应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a cold-resistant composite dust suppressant as well as a preparation method and application thereof. The preparation method of the cold-resistant composite dust suppressant comprises the following steps: adding xanthan gum powder and tara gum powder into an alkaline aqueous solution, and uniformly dispersing to obtain a first mixed solution; adding calcium magnesium acetate, konjac powder and a surfactant into the first mixed solution, and uniformly dispersing to obtain a second mixed solution; and removing moisture in the second mixed solution to obtain the cold-resistant composite dust suppressant with the gel structure. In an alkaline environment, xanthan gum powder, caesalpinia spinosa gum powder and konjac powder are used as raw materials, calcium magnesium acetate and a surfactant are added to form the cold-resistant composite dust suppressant with a gel structure, hydrogen bonds are formed among the materials for crosslinking and filling, a dynamic reaction occurs, and an embedding effect on water molecules is achieved; the water-retaining property is enhanced, the gel strength and viscosity are improved, and better dust inhibition capability is obtained."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供了一种耐寒复合抑尘剂及其制备方法和应用。该耐寒复合抑尘剂的制备方法包括：先将黄原胶粉末和刺云实胶粉末加入到碱性水溶液中分散均匀，得到第一混合溶液；然后将醋酸钙镁、魔芋精粉以及表面活性剂加入到第一混合溶液中分散均匀，得到第二混合溶液；将第二混合溶液中的水分去除得到凝胶结构的耐寒复合抑尘剂。本申请在碱性环境下，以黄原胶粉末、刺云实胶粉末以及魔芋精粉为原料，并加入醋酸钙镁以及表面活性剂形成凝胶结构的耐寒复合抑尘剂，多种材料之间形成氢键交联、填充、发生动态反应，对水分子有包埋作用，增强了保水性的同时提升凝胶强度及粘度，获得更好的粉尘抑制能力。"
                }
            ]
